## Monetization — Pro paywall (planned)

**Philosophy:** Free = track your collection accurately. Pro = act on it faster (refresh, alert, export, scan at scale).

| Feature | Free | Pro |
|---------|------|-----|
| Portfolio / watchlist size | 50 / 10 cards | Unlimited |
| Valuation on load | ✅ (cached + daily cron) | ✅ |
| **On-demand price refresh** | Limited (see above) | Unlimited |
| Comp match badges | ✅ | ✅ |
| Profit target + Ready to Sell | Basic (e.g. top 5 cards) | Full portfolio scan |
| Notifications / alerts | — or 1 watchlist alert | Unlimited + daily digest |
| Portfolio value chart | 30 days | Full history + CSV export |
| Grade tier comparison (Raw / 9 / 10) | — | ✅ |
| Bulk scan | — | ✅ |
| Saved searches / deal alerts | — | ✅ |

**Other strong Pro candidates:**
- **CSV / tax export** — high willingness-to-pay among serious collectors
- **Bulk scan mode** — direct API cost
- **"Fresh comp" alerts** — new eBay sold matching your `search_key`
- **Auctions ending soon** — watchlist-driven
- **Scan credit packs** — one-time IAP if PC/eBay costs spike (alternative to subscription)

**Weak paywall ideas (avoid):**
- Hiding market value behind paywall
- Fake stale prices on free tier to force upgrade
- Paywalling scan-to-add entirely (kills acquisition)

**Decision:** Build refresh-on-demand + quota **before** Stripe. Validates behavior and cost without payment integration.

---

User sets a **take-profit %** (default 20%). App scans portfolio and surfaces cards at/above target.

**Settings fields** (profiles or `user_preferences`):
- `target_profit_pct` (default 20)
- `profit_includes_fees` (default false)
- `estimated_sell_fee_pct` (default 16 — eBay + payment, user-tunable)

**Per card math:**
- `cost_basis` = `purchase_price_cents × quantity`
- `market_value` = grade-matched comp (from above stack)
- `profit_pct` = `(market − cost) / cost`
- `target_sell_price` = `cost × (1 + target_profit_pct/100)`
- **Net mode:** subtract fees before comparing to target

**Portfolio UI — "Ready to Sell" section:**
- 🎯 At target (≥ user's %)
- 📈 Getting close (within ~5% of target)
- ⏳ Hold (below target)

**Notifications (later):** "McGwire Tiffany PSA 9 crossed your 20% profit target."

Depends on **comp match accuracy first** — wrong market value = wrong sell signals.

