## Phased build order

### Phase 1 — Pricing accuracy (BLOCKER for everything else)
1. Fix grade-tier selection + tests on `pickPriceForGrade`
2. `CompMatchLevel` on `PortfolioValuation` + UI badges
3. Canonical card identity on add (`lookupCanonicalCard`)
4. Strict eBay title filtering (grade, variant, card #)
5. Backfill portfolio + aggregate `pricecharting_id`
6. Finish infra: daily `recompute-trends` pg_cron, honest null trends in UI

### Phase 2 — Trading dashboard
- Portfolio header: total value, today P/L, cost basis, unrealized gain
- `portfolio_snapshots` daily chart
- Best/worst performers; realized P/L via `sold_cards`
- **Ready to Sell** scanner (profit target from settings)
- **On-demand refresh** with free-tier quota + Pro unlimited (see Monetization)

### Phase 3 — Gamification (only after Phase 1)
- Daily digest push, milestone toasts, green-day streaks, confetti on meaningful gains
- "Hot hand" badge for best weekly performer

### Phase 4 — Roadmap remainder
Notifications, smarter scan, discover/deals, card detail upgrades, social, polish, monetization — see `roadmap.mdc`.

